        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3908479741" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7216743211795684603">This is the first book mentioned in a book by Colm Toibin and Carmen Callill: The 200 best novels in English since 1950. My intention is to read one of them now and again, if I can get hold of them.<br/>Of course I have read Christie&apos;s but I can&apos;t remember this one. It needs a change of reading, 20th century reading, but I enjoyed it. <br/>In the village of Chipping Cleghorn a murder is announced and indeed executed. The police isn&apos;t getting anywhere until Mrs. Marple comes to the scene.</span>
  <span id="freeText7216743211795684603" style="display:none">This is the first book mentioned in a book by Colm Toibin and Carmen Callill: The 200 best novels in English since 1950. My intention is to read one of them now and again, if I can get hold of them.<br />Of course I have read Christie's but I can't remember this one. It needs a change of reading, 20th century reading, but I enjoyed it. <br />In the village of Chipping Cleghorn a murder is announced and indeed executed. The police isn't getting anywhere until Mrs. Marple comes to the scene.</span>
